# Trajectory Log — Evidence Pack Template
# Step-by-step record of agent actions (tool calls, diffs, outputs)
# This log enables replay and audit of agent work.

# Format:
# [STEP N] <timestamp>
# Action: <what the agent did>
# Tool: <tool name> (if applicable)
# Input: <tool input summary>
# Output: <tool output summary>
# ---

# Example:
# [STEP 1] 2026-02-12T12:15:00+05:30
# Action: Read Project_Context.md
# Tool: view_file
# Input: D:\AI-Apps-In-Drive\App_Station\Score_Leads\Project_Context.md
# Output: 272 lines, product spec + operating charter
# ---
